data.description: This beautiful home located in South Carson City is a must-see. Property includes a brand new roof, fresh exterior paint, new front door, and front windows. Walking distance from Al Seeliger Elementary School. There is a separate living room, family room, and formal dining area on the 1st level. The home has large bedrooms as well as a beautifully landscaped backyard. Private and perfect for entertaining!
